1
00:00:49,920 --> 00:00:50,840
What are you doing?

2
00:00:51,000 --> 00:00:52,759
There were so many people around just now!

3
00:00:53,399 --> 00:00:55,439
Jiang Tiancai, have you lost your mind?

4
00:00:55,600 --> 00:00:57,439
Yes, I've lost my mind.

5
00:00:57,960 --> 00:00:58,640
In the past thirty-plus years,

6
00:00:58,719 --> 00:01:00,280
I've never been this crazy before.

7
00:01:02,119 --> 00:01:02,719
Do you know what the worst

8
00:01:02,799 --> 00:01:04,239
side effect of PEP is?

9
00:01:06,159 --> 00:01:08,280
Not dizziness, nausea, fever, or rashes.

10
00:01:08,599 --> 00:01:09,959
It's that every single night, I dream

11
00:01:10,040 --> 00:01:11,959
of you cooking in my kitchen.

12
00:01:13,319 --> 00:01:15,439
So there's no chance of any Reconciliation.

13
00:01:16,760 --> 00:01:18,280
I want you to know, crystal clear,

14
00:01:18,879 --> 00:01:19,439
that I...

15
00:01:19,959 --> 00:01:21,040
am in love with you,

16
00:01:21,400 --> 00:01:22,359
Tang Yi.

17
00:02:40,120 --> 00:02:40,759
Old Jiang

18
00:02:56,080 --> 00:02:57,360
Who's this?

19
00:02:58,879 --> 00:02:59,639
Do you know him?

20
00:02:59,879 --> 00:03:00,879
I've never seen this professor before.

21
00:03:01,039 --> 00:03:01,759
Jiang Zhaohe.

22
00:03:01,960 --> 00:03:03,479
The only one in the country to win

23
00:03:03,560 --> 00:03:05,159
the Golden Scalpel Award for Special Contribution three times in a row.

24
00:03:05,240 --> 00:03:06,759
A leading professor in Cardiac Surgery.

25
00:03:07,159 --> 00:03:08,479
A Cardiac Surgery expert.

26
00:03:08,800 --> 00:03:09,719
What's he doing here?

27
00:03:09,960 --> 00:03:10,680
Son.

28
00:03:11,639 --> 00:03:12,879
If work has worn you out,

29
00:03:13,159 --> 00:03:14,080
let's go home.

30
00:03:14,800 --> 00:03:15,759
Have your mom make you

31
00:03:15,919 --> 00:03:17,479
your favorite Red Braised Pork.

32
00:03:17,960 --> 00:03:19,520
We can play a few games of chess.

33
00:03:20,000 --> 00:03:21,719
Your son Xiaochun misses you so much.

34
00:03:21,919 --> 00:03:23,120
He asks for you all day long.

35
00:03:23,960 --> 00:03:25,919
Enough. Stop nagging.

36
00:03:26,319 --> 00:03:27,120
Let go.

37
00:03:28,120 --> 00:03:29,800
Our son still has work to do.

38
00:03:38,159 --> 00:03:39,199
Why didn't I

39
00:03:39,479 --> 00:03:40,360
think of that?

40
00:03:40,599 --> 00:03:41,599
No wonder Dr. Jiang

41
00:03:41,680 --> 00:03:43,280
is so accomplished at such a young age.

42
00:03:43,560 --> 00:03:45,280
He was born with great genes.

43
00:03:45,800 --> 00:03:47,439
It's because of Dr. Jiang's father.

44
00:03:47,639 --> 00:03:48,639
With a great dad,

45
00:03:49,120 --> 00:03:50,439
he doesn't have to work hard

46
00:03:50,759 --> 00:03:52,479
to get everything so easily.

47
00:03:53,599 --> 00:03:54,520
Truly enviable.

48
00:04:01,840 --> 00:04:02,800
What are you doing here?

49
00:04:09,639 --> 00:04:10,840
If I hadn't come,

50
00:04:12,000 --> 00:04:13,639
how could I see you here

51
00:04:14,240 --> 00:04:15,560
acting like someone else's son?

52
00:04:20,000 --> 00:04:21,920
That's because you failed as a father.

53
00:04:22,600 --> 00:04:23,519
Otherwise, your son

54
00:04:23,879 --> 00:04:25,519
wouldn't have to seek that bond with strangers.

55
00:04:33,879 --> 00:04:34,720
Tiancai.

56
00:04:35,720 --> 00:04:36,959
All these years,

57
00:04:37,839 --> 00:04:39,439
how much I've sacrificed for you,

58
00:04:40,079 --> 00:04:41,120
you know very well.

59
00:04:43,560 --> 00:04:44,439
I also know

60
00:04:45,839 --> 00:04:47,360
that because of your grandmother,

61
00:04:49,399 --> 00:04:50,639
you resent me, you hate me.

62
00:04:51,399 --> 00:04:52,639
I won't hold that against you.

63
00:04:53,480 --> 00:04:55,240
But you're an adult now.

64
00:04:56,040 --> 00:04:58,279
You can't keep ruining your own future.

65
00:04:58,959 --> 00:04:59,920
Sacrifice?

66
00:05:05,040 --> 00:05:06,199
The sacrifice you speak of

67
00:05:07,160 --> 00:05:08,160
was dumping seven-year-old me

68
00:05:09,040 --> 00:05:10,639
on my frail, sickly grandmother

69
00:05:12,240 --> 00:05:13,240
to go pursue further studies,

70
00:05:14,040 --> 00:05:15,199
gone for five whole years.

71
00:05:17,360 --> 00:05:19,319
Or how, on the rare times you came home,

72
00:05:20,480 --> 00:05:21,399
all you cared about was whether I was

73
00:05:21,480 --> 00:05:23,279
following the path you laid out,

74
00:05:23,560 --> 00:05:25,439
never caring about what I actually wanted?

75
00:05:32,879 --> 00:05:34,319
Just because, during the college entrance exam,

76
00:05:35,160 --> 00:05:36,399
I didn't meet your expectations

77
00:05:37,079 --> 00:05:37,920
and study Cardiac Surgery,

78
00:05:38,800 --> 00:05:40,519
you think I'm ruining my future.

79
00:05:41,040 --> 00:05:42,319
So if I decided right now

80
00:05:42,560 --> 00:05:43,879
to stay at this hospital

81
00:05:44,079 --> 00:05:45,199
and be a dentist for the rest of my life,

82
00:05:45,920 --> 00:05:47,759
wouldn't you feel you have no successor?

83
00:05:52,720 --> 00:05:55,000
So this is how you take revenge on me?

84
00:05:57,319 --> 00:05:59,120
Using the hands of a genius surgeon

85
00:06:00,720 --> 00:06:02,000
to do this kind of work?

86
00:06:04,160 --> 00:06:05,399
What's wrong with this work?

87
00:06:05,920 --> 00:06:07,439
Isn't it better than the

88
00:06:07,560 --> 00:06:08,800
scheming and plotting on the operating table?

89
00:06:18,199 --> 00:06:20,040
Back then, on her sickbed, your grandmother

90
00:06:20,120 --> 00:06:21,399
grabbed my hand and said,

91
00:06:22,360 --> 00:06:24,199
"Don't let him follow my path."

92
00:06:27,000 --> 00:06:28,160
Looking at it now,

93
00:06:28,959 --> 00:06:30,600
she really was worrying for nothing.

94
00:06:31,000 --> 00:06:32,279
You have no right to mention her.

95
00:06:34,199 --> 00:06:35,439
The name Jiang Zhaohe,

96
00:06:35,959 --> 00:06:36,720
to me,

97
00:06:37,079 --> 00:06:39,000
means nothing more than a stranger.

98
00:06:40,720 --> 00:06:41,680
If it weren't for those so-called...

99
00:06:41,959 --> 00:06:43,120
so-called pursuits of yours,

100
00:06:44,759 --> 00:06:46,560
Grandma wouldn't have left me so soon.

101
00:06:48,000 --> 00:06:48,959
Pursuits?

102
00:06:51,199 --> 00:06:52,199
My pursuit

103
00:06:52,480 --> 00:06:53,879
was to bring our country's medical technology

104
00:06:54,319 --> 00:06:56,160
up to international standards five years sooner.

105
00:06:56,240 --> 00:06:56,959
You know what?

106
00:06:57,959 --> 00:06:58,920
I have a Clear conscience.

107
00:07:02,959 --> 00:07:03,560
And you?

108
00:07:05,199 --> 00:07:06,480
What is it that you pursue?

109
00:07:06,839 --> 00:07:08,120
What I pursue,

110
00:07:09,680 --> 00:07:11,279
you'll never understand in your entire life.

111
00:07:18,639 --> 00:07:19,360
Tiancai.

112
00:07:21,800 --> 00:07:23,079
Sorry, I didn't know you had company.

113
00:07:23,199 --> 00:07:23,720
I'll just go.

114
00:07:23,759 --> 00:07:24,480
Tang Yi.

115
00:07:29,519 --> 00:07:30,120
Perfect timing.

116
00:07:30,720 --> 00:07:31,560
Let me introduce you.

117
00:07:32,079 --> 00:07:34,040
This is my girlfriend, Tang Yi.

118
00:07:55,879 --> 00:07:57,240
Didn't you say the surgery was a success?

119
00:07:57,439 --> 00:07:59,439
Then why is she gone? Why?

120
00:08:23,680 --> 00:08:24,240
Tang Yi.

121
00:08:24,759 --> 00:08:25,480
Stop right there.

122
00:08:27,399 --> 00:08:29,319
Jiang Tiancai, let me tell you.

123
00:08:29,600 --> 00:08:30,959
The only one who belongs by your side

124
00:08:31,240 --> 00:08:32,200
is Lin Fei'er.

125
00:08:32,559 --> 00:08:34,080
You're of equal standing, and know each other inside out.

126
00:08:34,320 --> 00:08:35,840
She's the perfect match for you.

127
00:08:50,960 --> 00:08:52,480
Ignoring a child's malocclusion,

128
00:08:52,799 --> 00:08:54,080
thinking it'll fix itself with adult teeth,

129
00:08:54,480 --> 00:08:55,919
is a huge misconception.

130
00:08:56,639 --> 00:08:57,759
A child's malocclusion

131
00:08:58,120 --> 00:09:00,559
not only affects their facial appearance,

132
00:09:01,000 --> 00:09:03,080
but may also impair chewing function,

133
00:09:03,440 --> 00:09:04,679
affecting digestion and absorption.

134
00:09:05,039 --> 00:09:07,600
It can even have negative effects

135
00:09:07,720 --> 00:09:09,039
on the child's mental health.

136
00:09:09,759 --> 00:09:10,360
Parents

137
00:09:10,799 --> 00:09:12,399
should take their child's malocclusion

138
00:09:12,720 --> 00:09:14,080
seriously,

139
00:09:14,440 --> 00:09:15,600
and promptly seek

140
00:09:15,840 --> 00:09:17,159
help from an Orthodontics specialist.

